verbose_text: Supplementing l-isoleucine in diets also stimulated the mRNA expressions of IFN-beta, IFN-gamma, IL-10, IL-1beta, and TNF-alpha in the ileum and mesenteric lymph nodes, although to different extents (P < 0.05 or P < 0.10, Table XREF_TABLE), and further enhanced the mRNA expressions of IFN-beta, IFN-gamma, IL-10, IL-1beta, and/or TNF-alpha in the ileum and mesenteric lymph nodes of weaned piglets infected by RV (P < 0.05, Table XREF_TABLE).
